<!-- This file contains basic concepts of Web Technology and JavaScript -->

•	What is Web Technology?
--> Web Technology is used to create and run differnt web page,websites and interact with web applications.
    It is also used to make webpages more interactive.
    <!-- 
    1. Web Technology is a collection of tools, languages and techniques used to build websites and web applications.
    2. It includes technologies like HTML, CSS, JavaScript, databases.
    3.It allows users to access information through the internet using browser.
    -->

•	Real-time examples of Web Technology
--> There are various examples like Amazon, Flipkart, Myntra, Instagram, Ajio, etc.
<!-- 
1. These websites use web technologies to provide the online services.
2. E commerce websites like the Amazon and Flipkart use the web technology for online shopping.
3. Social media platforms like the Instagram use the web technology for communication and sharing the media.
4. Every website or web application we use daily built using web technology. -->

•	What is JavaScript?
--> Javascript is a programming language which is used to make web pages more interactive.
<!-- 
1. Javascript is a client side scripting language.
2. It helps to add the dynamic behavior to static pages.
3. Using Javascript we can handle the events like button clicks forms, validation , animations etc.
4. It is one of the core technologies of web development along with HTML and CSS. -->

•	Which file extension is used for JavaScript?
--> The file extension usedfor javascript is '.js' .
<!-- 
1. Example: Activity.js, main.js -->

•	Why do we use Node.js?
--> Node.js is used ti run javascript code outside the browser. 
<!-- 
1. Nodejs is a runtime environment for the Javascript.
2. It is helpful for creating the web servers, APIs and the real time applications 
3. We can run the JavaScript code inside the browser also , by writing it in console. -->
